-- ALTER VIEW gso.dim_gco
-- AS
SELECT
[REGION]
,[CLUSTER]
,[COUNTRY]
,[SLSL]
,[FLSL]
,[CITY]
,[BUSINESS_UNIT]
,[FIELD_VISIT_COACHING_DATE]
,[BRAND]
,[TOTAL_NUMBER_CALLS_OBSERVED]
,[NUMBER_OF_GSO]
,[FLSL_MOTIVATIONAL_INSPIRATIONAL_ENVIRONMENT]
,[FLSL_SALES_REP_AGREE_GOAL]
,[COACHING_GOAL_SEQUENTIAL_PREVIOUS_ACTION]
,[FLSL_SALES_REP_MENTION_CURRENT_PERFORMANCE]
,[POTENTIAL_IMPACT_CURRENT_PERFORMANCE]
,[FLSL_SALES_REP_BLOCK_CURRENT_PERFORMANCE]
,[SALES_REP_SOLUTIONS_UNBLOCK_BARRIERS]
,[FLSL_SALES_REP_SOLUTIONS_UNBLOCK_BARRIERS_IMPACT]
,[FLSL_OFFERS_ALTERNATIVE_SOLUTIONS]
,[EXPLORE_SALES_REP_NEXT_STEPS]
,[MANAGER_ASKS_SALES_REP_SUPPORT_NEEDS]
,[BUILDS_PLAN_SUCCESS_MEASURES]
,[IMPORTANT_ACTION_IMPROVE_CAPABILITY_MAPS_TOP_SKILL]
,[DETERMINES_COACHING_STYLE_FLEXES_COACHING_STYLE]
,[QUESTIONS_ACTIVE_LISTENING_FEEDBACK_SBI]
,[ACTION_PLANS]
FROM
    OPENROWSET(
        BULK 'https://gsksynapseaccount.dfs.core.windows.net/gskoutputfiles/GSO/dimensao_gco.parquet',
        FORMAT='PARQUET'
    ) WITH (
        [REGION]                                     VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[CLUSTER]									 VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[COUNTRY]									  VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[SLSL]										  VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[FLSL]										  VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[CITY]										  VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[BUSINESS_UNIT]							  VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[FIELD_VISIT_COACHING_DATE]				  DATE
,[BRAND]									  VARCHAR(250) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[TOTAL_NUMBER_CALLS_OBSERVED]				  SMALLINT
,[NUMBER_OF_GSO]                              INT
,[FLSL_MOTIVATIONAL_INSPIRATIONAL_ENVIRONMENT]          SMALLINT
,[FLSL_SALES_REP_AGREE_GOAL]                                SMALLINT
,[COACHING_GOAL_SEQUENTIAL_PREVIOUS_ACTION]    SMALLINT
,[FLSL_SALES_REP_MENTION_CURRENT_PERFORMANCE]    SMALLINT
,[POTENTIAL_IMPACT_CURRENT_PERFORMANCE]    SMALLINT
,[FLSL_SALES_REP_BLOCK_CURRENT_PERFORMANCE]    SMALLINT
,[SALES_REP_SOLUTIONS_UNBLOCK_BARRIERS]    SMALLINT
,[FLSL_SALES_REP_SOLUTIONS_UNBLOCK_BARRIERS_IMPACT]    SMALLINT
,[FLSL_OFFERS_ALTERNATIVE_SOLUTIONS]    SMALLINT
,[EXPLORE_SALES_REP_NEXT_STEPS]    SMALLINT
,[MANAGER_ASKS_SALES_REP_SUPPORT_NEEDS]    SMALLINT
,[BUILDS_PLAN_SUCCESS_MEASURES]    SMALLINT
,[IMPORTANT_ACTION_IMPROVE_CAPABILITY_MAPS_TOP_SKILL]    SMALLINT
,[DETERMINES_COACHING_STYLE_FLEXES_COACHING_STYLE]   SMALLINT
,[QUESTIONS_ACTIVE_LISTENING_FEEDBACK_SBI]    VARCHAR(MAX) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[ACTION_PLANS] VARCHAR(MAX) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8 ) as ROW
